{"tid":581022,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"跨界照做王者！Kobe贏埋奧斯卡","createTime":"2018-03-05T03:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T03:53:09.000Z","uid":153600,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef258300cfecc4a8f569795d26966ea8a7708ae2","tid":581022,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=KOyLHZc6IGti%2B7ug2mKjnYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=847e20df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】已退役的NBA球星高比拜仁連電影界也征服！在周日奧斯卡贏得最佳動畫短片獎。<br />\n<br />\n39歲的高比拜仁（Kobe Bryant）於2016年結束20年NBA生涯，2015年在《Players Tribune》撰寫了一封離開球場的感人信件，同時製作了一條動畫短片《籃球日記》。<br />\n<br />\n結果跟基連堅尼製作公司合作的《籃球日記》，在周日榮獲奧斯卡最佳動畫短片獎。跟太太盛裝出席的高比拜仁在領獎時笑言：「仍為籃球員，我們應該收聲之後運球離去，我很高興可以做得多一點點。多謝奧斯卡給予我這個榮譽。」<br />\n<br />\n在早前的訪問中，Kobe曾表示，決定跟曾製作不少迪士尼動畫的基連堅尼製作公司合作，全因對方不懂籃球：「這樣他們才會注重所有細節。當你用全新的角度去看籃球，就會留意每一個位置。」"},{"pid":"d8f7ed9133e57df68724da9e129ef29119d91f33","tid":581022,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:25:55.000Z","msg":"感動世人"},{"pid":"e046cda2d86483e9e356c2ebceb507c97d0b2498","tid":581022,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:31:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"894ad84cbac34363089d36cca16f9a7012798bc5","tid":581022,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:46:05.000Z","msg":"正式Kobe 宣布已經超越mj<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362c5b982eaea6432ca59e1bfef59cc6dab60952","tid":581022,"uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"894ad84cbac34363089d36cca16f9a7012798bc5","tid":581022,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:46:05.000Z","msg":"正式Kobe 宣布已經超越mj<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:53:09.000Z","msg":"mj : 0 oscar<br />\nkobe : 1 oscar<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nkobe&gt;mj<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}